The '''Combat Umbrella''' was a device used by specialized [[Clone commando/Legends|clone commandos]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], including the members of [[High Orbit Precision Entry Squad|H.O.P.E. Squad]]. It was used to slow descent when making high orbit precision entries such as attacking a repulsor platform.

